                    <p>
                        i use <a href="https://archlinux.org/">arch</a> for my desktop + <a href="https://cachyos.org/">cachyos</a> (same thing anyways bweh) for my laptop. my phone runs <a href="https://grapheneos.org/">grapheneos</a> & u should use it too!
